captions.text: - Getting a Text from an Unknown Number

- I'm sorry I forgot your beautiful
name... What was it again?
What's her name? What's her name?
- haha this isn't my first time over
Wow, was I really that smooth oh my gosh!
- Want me to grab you a coffee on the way?

- Venti iced coffee
with 2 pumps of vanilla
- I must've told you a lot last night haha

- Not really but I can't wait
to hear about EVERYTHING!

I'm not gonna tell you
everything about me.

- Are we still meeting up
with your parents today?
- Almost here? Almost here, oh my God.
- Justin, what are you doing here?
she's about to be here right now!
and I got a new number.
- I don't care, you need to go!
- She should be here any minute.

title: When You Get A Text From An Unknown Number
